OL,3,CMan blinded in glass attack reunited
OL,4,Cwith family after six months
OL,6,FA man left blind after being glassed
OL,7,Fon a night out in Leeds has finally
OL,8,Fbeen reunited with his Australian
OL,9,Ffamily after six months.
OL,11,FMatthew Syron, 32, has been unable to
OL,12,Freturn to Australia since he was
OL,13,Fattacked in the city centre in
OL,14,FDecember.
OL,16,FHe said: "It's been amazing,
OL,17,Fespecially seeing my two kids, it
OL,18,Fchanges everything. It's been a long
OL,19,Fsix months.
