OL,3,CMan blinded in glass attack reunited
OL,4,Cwith family after six months
OL,6,F"I'm very tough but I'm glad I've got
OL,7,Fthe family here now and hopefully I
OL,8,Fcan just recover and get home."
OL,10,FThe 32-year-old has already had
OL,11,Fsurgery on his eyes and has regained
OL,12,Fsome sight in his right eye.
OL,14,FBut he does not know if further
OL,15,Fsurgery will improve his sight.
OL,17,FMr Syron, who lives in Australia with
OL,18,Fhis fiancee and two children, was
OL,19,Fvisiting family in his home city when
OL,20,Fthe attack happened on Boxing Day.
