OL,3,CMan blinded in glass attack reunited
OL,4,Cwith family after six months
OL,6,FBut now the family has been reunited
OL,7,Ffor the first time in nearly seven
OL,8,Fmonths.
OL,10,FHis wife Keone Rawiri said: "It feels
OL,11,Famazing to be together as a family
OL,12,Funit as a team and just have Matt be
OL,13,Fthere as I'm putting the kids to bed.
OL,14,FIt's the little things you miss.
