OL,3,CMan blinded in glass attack reunited
OL,4,Cwith family after six months
OL,6,F"It's extremely hard - heartbreaking,
OL,7,Fdevastating it's everything that you
OL,8,Fcould imagine that you don't want to
OL,9,Fimagine as a parent as a wife. It rips
OL,10,Fyour soul apart. We just have to keep
OL,11,Fpushing because we can't go back to
OL,12,Fthe past and change it."
