OL,3,CMan blinded in glass attack reunited
OL,4,Cwith family after six months
OL,6,FMatthew, added: "There's highs and
OL,7,Flows. It's very tough to take from
OL,8,Fwhere I was at to where I am now. It's
OL,9,Fa hard pill to swallow going blind.
OL,10,FHaving the kids here has been tough -
OL,11,Fmy son wanting to play football and
OL,12,Ftennis with him and I can't play with
OL,13,Fhim and he's asking 'daddy why can't
OL,14,Fyou play with me?' But it is what it
OL,15,Fis these are the cards I've been dealt
OL,16,FI just have to keep moving forward."
OL,18,FIn March this year 37-year-old Gareth
OL,19,FDean was jailed for more than 10 years
OL,20,Ffor the unprovoked attack.
